  "description": "<i>Beyblade: Metal Fusion</i> is an 3D action game based on the Beyblade: Metal Fusion animated series. Beybladers are knocked unconscious after losing their match in the Nosferatu Tournament held at the Beyblade colosseum. The player has to find out who is behind this.<br><br>In the game the player will control a spinning top called a Beyblade. This Beyblade has to battle other Beyblades and can do all kinds of moves and special attacks. The game offers a story mode, battle mode (via Wi-Fi connection) and the Bey garage where the spinning top can be upgraded. The game offers over 19 playable characters, most of whom have to be unlocked first. Players can also use voice commands with the microphone of the DS.",
